<div class="apidocs row">
  <div class="col-xs-9">
    <div class='page-header'>
      <h1><span class="initialism">POST</span> /api/v1/taxa2lca
        <br>
        <small>Returns the lowest common ancestor for a given list of taxon id's.</small>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <p>
      This will actually calculate the lowest common ancestor of all the lineages of all the taxon ids passed via the input paramater.
    </p>

    <h2 id="request">Request</h2>

    <h2 id="response">Response</h2>

    <h2 id="examples">Examples</h2>
    <pre class="prettyprint">
$ curl -X POST -H &quot;Accept: application/json&quot; api.unipept.ugent.be/api/v1/taxa2lca -d &#39;input[0]=816&#39; -d &#39;input[1]=124&#39;
{&quot;taxon_id&quot;:2,&quot;taxon_name&quot;:&quot;Bacteria&quot;,&quot;taxon_parent_id&quot;:131567,&quot;taxon_rank&quot;:&quot;superkingdom&quot;}
    </pre>

  <h2 id="parameters">Parameters</h2>
  <table class='table'>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Param name</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <strong>input </strong><br>
          <small>required</small>
        </td>
        <td>
          <p>List of input taxon ids</p>
          <br>
          Value: Must be an array of any type
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <strong>extra </strong><br>
          <small>optional</small>
        </td>
        <td>
          <p>Request extra information such as the entire lineage</p>
          <br>
          Value: Must be one of: true, false.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <strong>names </strong><br>
          <small>optional</small>
        </td>
        <td>
          <p>Include the lineage names</p>
          <br>
          Value: Must be one of: true, false.
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
